<section id="itsm_provenanceRecords">
    <title>provenanceRecords</title>
    <para>Provenance Records - a standoff wrapper element to group any number of single Provenance Record elements related to the same span of source or target content.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Contains:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
      <member>- One or more <olink targetdoc="itsm_provenanceRecord.xml" targetptr="itsm_provenanceRecord"><code>&lt;itsm_provenanceRecord></code></olink>
            elements</member>
        
    </simplelist>
  
  <para><emphasis>Parents:</emphasis></para>
  
  <simplelist>
    <member>- <olink targetdoc="../structural/unit.xml"
      targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink></member>
    <member>- <olink targetdoc="../structural/group.xml"
      targetptr="group"><code>&lt;group></code></olink></member>
    <member>- <olink targetdoc="../structural/file.xml"
      targetptr="file"><code>&lt;file></code></olink></member>
  </simplelist>
  

    <para><emphasis>Attributes:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
      <member>- <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_id.xml" targetptr="itsm_id">
        <code>xml:id</code>
      </olink>, <glossterm>required</glossterm>
    </member>
      <!--  not allowed on ITS stand off elements <member>-<olink targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_annotatorsRef.xml"
        targetptr="itsm_annotatorsRef">
        <code>annotatorsRef</code></olink>,
        <glossterm>optional</glossterm></member>-->
        
    </simplelist>
<!-- This Constraint would be too strong as a MUST, it would invalidate XLIFF Documents with orphaned Provenance Records. But this can happen because the references can be removed by core only Modifiers.-->
<itemizedlist>
  <title>Constraints</title>
  <listitem>
    <para>Each <link linkend="itsm_provenanceRecords">provenanceRecords</link> element
          <glossterm>should</glossterm> be referenced by at least one <olink
          targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_provenanceRecordsRef.xml"
          targetptr="itsm_provenanceRecordsRef"><code>provenanceRecordsRef</code></olink> attribute
        from the common parent element or one of the common parent's descendants as per Constraints
        for the <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/itsm/itsm_provenanceRecordsRef.xml"
          targetptr="itsm_provenanceRecordsRef"><code>provenanceRecordsRef</code></olink>
        attribute.</para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Processing Requirements</title>
    <listitem>
      <para><firstterm>Modifiers</firstterm> detecting an orphaned <link
          linkend="itsm_provenanceRecords">provenanceRecords</link> element
          <glossterm>may</glossterm> delete that <link linkend="itsm_provenanceRecords"
          >provenanceRecords</link> element.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  
</section>
